\f2\i\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \strokec2 China also leveraged \cb3 deepfake \cb1 technology to create convincing and false audiovisual content, making it challenging for the public to distinguish between genuine and manipulated information. By doing so, they aimed to erode trust in official sources and create an environment where disinformation could thrive.
